item.description:
[1:1] Now after the death of Saul, when David, having come back from the destruction of the Amalekites, had been in Ziklag for two days;
[1:2] On the third day a man came from Saul&rsquo;s tents, with his clothing out of order and earth on his head: and when he came to David, he went down on the earth and gave him honour.
[1:3] And David said to him, Where have you come from?
